## STACK OBRIGATГ“RIA

```
Backend  в†’ FastAPI (Python 3.11) + SQLAlchemy async + PostgreSQL + Alembic
Auth     в†’ JWT com python-jose + bcrypt (passlib) + SlowAPI (rate limit)
Frontend в†’ Next.js 14 (App Router) + React 18 + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS
Infra    в†’ Docker Compose (api + admin + site + postgres)
DNS      в†’ Cloudflare API v4
Git      в†’ GitHub API (fork de template repo)
Email    в†’ aiosmtplib (SMTP) ou SendGrid
Cripto   в†’ cryptography.fernet (chaves de integraГ§ГЈo por tenant)
```

Nunca sugira trocar de stack. Nunca use Express, Django, Prisma, ou outras alternativas.

