## BANCO DE DADOS

### PadrГµes absolutos
- Todos os IDs sГЈo `String(32)`, gerados com `uuid.uuid4().hex` (UUID sem hГ­fens)
- Todas as FKs seguem o mesmo tipo `String(32)`
- Timestamps: `DateTime(timezone=True)`, sempre com `server_default=func.now()`
- Enums: usar `SQLAlchemy Enum` com `values_callable` para compatibilidade
- Migrations: arquivos em `apps/api/alembic/versions/`, nomenclatura `NNN_descricao.py`

### Tabelas existentes (migrations 001вЂ“013)
`users`, `tenants`, `user_tenants`, `plans`, `niches`, `modules`, `plan_niche_modules`, `blog_posts`, `site_pages`, `property_items`, `leads`, `schedule_items`, `media_items`, `catalog_audit_logs`, `workspace_externals`, `integration_apps`

### Tabelas a criar (migrations 014+)
- 014: `tenants` (ALTER) вЂ” subdomain, custom_domain, cf_record_id, provisioning_status, provisioned_at, git_repo_url, welcome_email_sent
- 015: `briefings` вЂ” client_name, client_email, plan_code, niche_code, slug_requested, status, tenant_id (FK nullable), etc.
- 016: `tenant_integrations` вЂ” tenant_id, integration_code, config_encrypted, config_public (UniqueConstraint tenant_id + integration_code)
- 017: `provisioning_logs` вЂ” briefing_id, step_number, step_name, status, message
- 018вЂ“024: `review_items`, `team_members`, `faq_categories`/`faq_items`, `menu_categories`/`menu_items`, `locations`, `newsletter_subscribers`, `stripe_products`

