## INTEGRAГ‡Г•ES

- **Por tenant:** tenant_integrations; sensГ­veis criptografados (Fernet). CГіdigos: google_oauth, meta_pixel, stripe, google_maps, whatsapp, mailchimp, ga4, google_reviews, calendly.
- **Plataforma:** CF_*, GIT_*, SMTP_*, SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL, ENCRYPTION_KEY em /platform/integrations.

